{"tid":2288593,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"「巨肺」唱LIVE竟然咪嘴？？","createTime":"2020-11-16T15:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T16:10:18.000Z","uid":69836,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62a6aaa6156f8b55eaa2d96f09573274ff0375d2","tid":2288593,"uid":69836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=akSyoa2eB9g&amp;ab_channel=ViuTV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DakSyoa2eB9g%26ab_channel%3DViuTV&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fuyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=77bd0851\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=akSyoa2eB9g&amp;ab_channel=ViuTV</a><br />\n頭幾句聽得出係LIVE, 因為夠低音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔扮下真唱一陣點上高音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一去到鏡頭過場  1:00<br />\n啲音色就開始唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似播CD咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後鏡頭9成時間都係影個咪係個嘴前面 幫佢遮住<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fzHPL0D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfzHPL0D.png&h=5a9fce6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gSiBoBC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgSiBoBC.png&h=f68fde05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一係就勁遠鏡 (屌你唔好再細啲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FNdhC61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFNdhC61.png&h=b908b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2rrie1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2rrie1K.png&h=ee11dc88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一係就有啲陰影係個嘴到<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GUEx3QZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGUEx3QZ.png&h=1961ce93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n穿煲就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係得拉高音個啲比你見到0.1秒個嘴, 驚你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pCBtbWY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpCBtbWY.png&h=1659b1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好不幸地 1:56秒唱「探戈」已經聽到個音同個嘴已經有DELAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2:00-2:02 「宇宙和宇宙」係成句都唔對嘴形, 問你死未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個攝影師我諗都盡咗全力<br />\n2:45同埋3:05淨係比個角落頭位影個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁嘅拍攝技術我唔相信電視台會咁做 你明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3EPXnOG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3EPXnOG.png&h=83d4f1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3EPXnOG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3EPXnOG.png&h=83d4f1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗攝影師心諗你唱到咁點幫你遮 唉不如成個樣幫你遮住算啦<br />\n<br />\n去到最尾要扮返真唱 比多幾個CLOSEUP你等觀眾易啲信<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E0ZTKSz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FE0ZTKSz.png&h=2bc78352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可惜穿曬煲兜唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7695cf681fe36b94045040c82b1eb331dc3dba86","tid":2288593,"uid":374986,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fe769e26321b58f56db4a384f08f279a0d760f","tid":2288593,"uid":374986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7695cf681fe36b94045040c82b1eb331dc3dba86","tid":2288593,"uid":374986,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"冇嘢啦睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e32c0f42daaa442c7e125850ae5161652dfce7b","tid":2288593,"uid":163492,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:06:42.000Z","msg":"幾難聽下"},{"pid":"b19b3935c811be8cd9c5e73e4ad1c4bb0a4cab00","tid":2288593,"uid":55800,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"特登去睇多次YouTube link<br />\n首先，2:00-2:02冇唔啱嘴形喎<br />\n成條片明明好多位包括：<br />\n1:42-1:47<br />\n2:09-2:14<br />\n2:35-2:40<br />\n都清楚影到個嘴，樓主就講到攝影師真係特登左遮右遮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我勸大家都去睇下條片先下判斷，唔好淨係信樓主片面之詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67c47d2e487da7462a5f8cd30f1d93f71a10811","tid":2288593,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"咪唔咪嘴都睇好多既<br />\n<br />\n呢條片擺明係咪哂全首<br />\n<br />\n你一開始睇佢係咁chok咪但啲震音咁穩定就唔合理<br />\n<br />\n加上全條片把聲個修飾味好重，擺明係cd聲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2b0a4ce736ea878c610da140ed91757eedb216","tid":2288593,"uid":126507,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b19b3935c811be8cd9c5e73e4ad1c4bb0a4cab00","tid":2288593,"uid":55800,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"特登去睇多次YouTube link<br />\n首先，2:00-2:02冇唔啱嘴形喎<br />\n成條片明明好多位包括：<br />\n1:42-1:47<br />\n2:09-2:14<br />\n2:35-2:40<br />\n都清楚影到個嘴，樓主就講到攝影師真係特登左遮右遮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我勸大家都去睇下條片先下判斷，唔好淨係信樓主片面之詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"對位歌手本身冇乜意見 <br />\n但佢呢條live成條都係咪嘴的<br />\n成首歌嘅嘴形同聲音本身就冇match到<br />\n最決定性嘅位置係低音  47秒  戀愛  呢到直頭close up大頭咪錯左  <br />\n加上首歌音質根本就修哂音  唔係live嘅音質黎<br />\n可能樓主態度比較差  但佢講嘅咪嘴係事實"},{"pid":"fb16bc0fb7a9cba67b5509e4dfefb5b0a102128a","tid":2288593,"uid":69836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:42:08.000Z","msg":"CD巨肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f82b24d461c11d20933eaf654026def44ddebe","tid":2288593,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:43:07.000Z","msg":"巨肺只有gem"},{"pid":"a573e322503afa6526f289cb5f7cd8fa16954a9d","tid":2288593,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:43:46.000Z","msg":"佢都唔係科班出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550098fce78ff47216e8e2113c36e63051e9f0be","tid":2288593,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"爆肺"},{"pid":"089e10cb2a6486acb00e3b7faf0bb8e44fca1433","tid":2288593,"uid":69836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f82b24d461c11d20933eaf654026def44ddebe","tid":2288593,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:43:07.000